    <b>Display Preferences</b>
    • Temperature unit selection
    • Time format (24h/12h)
    • Date format options
    • User-friendly display
end note

note right of MaxPoints
    <b>Chart Settings</b>
    • Buffer size control
    • Update frequency
    • Error handling option
    • Performance tuning
end note

note right of DefaultInterval
    <b>Data Settings</b>
    • Periodic interval
    • Retention policy
    • Auto-save toggle
    • Data management
end note

note right of LocalStorage
    <b>Browser Storage</b>
    • Persistent settings
    • Survives reload
    • Per-domain storage
    • Key-value pairs
end note

note right of Save
    <b>Settings Actions</b>
    • Load: from localStorage
    • Save: to localStorage
    • Export: JSON download
    • Import: JSON upload
    • Restore: factory defaults
end note

@enduml